# Design system (mandatory)

Read and obey [design-spec.md](design-spec.md) before any UI change.

## Non-negotiables

- Accent: deep forest green `#1F4D3A` (`primary-container`). Brand/ink: `#023625` (`primary`).
- Fonts: Libre Caslon Text for headlines/brand; Inter for body/labels. No Geist for UI chrome.
- Light theme + linen background only. No dark-mode-first, purple, glow, or rounded-full status pills.
- App shell is **top nav** (max 1200px), not a left sidebar.
- Cards only for interactive containers. Empty states: one headline, one sentence, one CTA.
- Stage markers are squares (`rounded-none`), not pills.

## Token source of truth

CSS variables in `app/globals.css`. Prefer Tailwind theme colors mapped there (`bg-primary-container`, `text-on-surface`, etc.). Do not invent parallel hex values.

## If unsure

Match the Stitch HTML patterns documented in `design-spec.md`. Do not "improve" the palette.
